Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.31,0:00:03.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无限的时间将跳动停止
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.94,0:00:05.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人们悄声无息地燃烧着
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.03,0:00:08.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有任何人注意到
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.69,0:00:11.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界已经脱轨
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.69,0:00:13.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被红世之火所包围
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.01,0:01:47.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好了 悠二
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.05,0:01:49.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一点点的把力量传给我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.22,0:01:50.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.26,0:01:52.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.35,0:01:52.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.32,0:02:12.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,8)}{\bord2\1c&H3535FF&\3c&HCFCFCF&}悠二和夏娜和KISS
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.97,0:02:17.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翅膀已经能很轻松地成型了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.02,0:02:18.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总算是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.90,0:02:37.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏娜 时间到了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.03,0:02:40.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 那今天到此为止
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.62,0:02:54.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,12点 零时迷子么  
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.45,0:02:57.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,力量回复了好是好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.53,0:02:58.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但着感觉总  
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.37,0:03:00.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要习惯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.88,0:03:01.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.15,0:03:06.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微有点  肚子饿呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.65,0:03:09.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去下面吃点什么吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.40,0:03:19.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是啥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.71,0:03:20.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电视剧重播
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.36,0:03:22.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电视剧 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.77,0:03:24.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是指编出来的故事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.32,0:03:25.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.28,0:03:26.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要关掉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.28,0:03:28.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.48,0:03:34.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理惠 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.92,0:03:50.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.44,0:03:52.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.49,0:03:54.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么那家伙被打了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.31,0:03:58.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是  一般突然要被KISS了总会不愿意吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.92,0:03:59.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是KISS这种程度 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.89,0:04:01.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,程  程度
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.81,0:04:02.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.95,0:04:25.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家  大家都在看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.61,0:04:27.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好怕啊 泰莉亚露
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.31,0:04:29.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧的 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.30,0:04:40.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因为你们这样的行动和华丽的衣服才引人注目的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.27,0:04:46.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 花朵要绽放难道还需要犹豫吗  修德耐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.21,0:04:53.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不希望\N听你这个被我的摇篮庭院所保护的家伙说这种臭屁的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.15,0:04:58.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs20}摇篮庭院<cradle garden> "爱染他"泰莉亚露的自在法 \h可以将在这个世界存在的红世之徒的异样感完全隐藏\N战斗时和封绝拥有相同机能 对普通的火焰之雾来说犹如蚁地狱般的空间
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.43,0:05:07.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  喂  泰莉亚露  可以吃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.73,0:05:09.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.63,0:05:12.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但 能否请再稍等会
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.14,0:05:15.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么自在式
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.96,0:05:18.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎快发现哥哥寻找的东西了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.15,0:05:20.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以做好准备
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.85,0:05:23.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难得才找到 被谁抢走的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.90,0:05:25.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可就不好了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.73,0:05:27.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为  为了不给别人拿走
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.22,0:05:28.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以要关起来对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.65,0:05:30.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用我们的摇篮
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.65,0:05:39.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.02,0:05:43.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请吃了那个以外的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.82,0:05:46.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.92,0:05:53.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 知不知道八音盒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.04,0:05:57.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs25}八音盒:爱染他所持有的宝具 不管如何复杂的自在法 一旦装进便能无限使用
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.08,0:05:57.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八音盒 是指音乐盒么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.52,0:05:59.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 虽然一般都是这么叫
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.47,0:06:04.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但称为八音盒的话作为音乐来说不是更优雅些么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.76,0:06:10.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是和这个自在法一起使用的宝具吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.16,0:06:13.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸣响的旋律非常好听哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.42,0:06:26.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现  现在还玩躲避球什么的  
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.60,0:06:33.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.33,0:06:36.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  一点事也没
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.05,0:06:53.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.16,0:06:54.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,田中
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.03,0:07:10.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好大的雨啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.93,0:07:12.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但还好中止了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.08,0:07:15.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果再那样继续的话可糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.29,0:07:16.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.38,0:07:17.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.21,0:07:19.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大姐 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.43,0:07:20.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.17,0:07:22.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个可算重伤了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.35,0:07:25.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 坂井
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.60,0:07:26.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.28,0:07:28.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于平井同学的事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.98,0:07:30.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.01,0:07:32.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  虽然你们经常一起来上学
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.34,0:07:34.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  怎么说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.61,0:07:37.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有没发生什么事 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.48,0:07:40.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 没没 什么也没有
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.54,0:07:42.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.85,0:07:57.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然说只不过是接吻嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.51,0:07:59.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但还是没那么简单的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.18,0:08:01.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊~~这个我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.04,0:08:04.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是随便的话 稍后就会滑溜溜的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.75,0:08:07.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是这个意思啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.84,0:08:11.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么说呢 总觉得KISS也很重要
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.12,0:08:11.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.10,0:08:14.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啊  你是说这个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.67,0:08:17.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  说的是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.53,0:08:30.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,KISS  昨天悠二的感觉也很怪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.29,0:08:43.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教我的并没错
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.68,0:08:47.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.05,0:08:50.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛 原来在这啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.80,0:08:52.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在查什么 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.43,0:08:54.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.53,0:08:56.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.39,0:08:59.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么 也不是什么大不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.20,0:09:09.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用担心也没问题的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.78,0:09:10.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,池同学
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.06,0:09:14.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才也说了吧 只是和平井同学关系好而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.41,0:09:15.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没恋爱的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.96,0:09:20.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.76,0:09:21.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.50,0:09:25.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大姐 我们回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.96,0:09:27.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的状态如何
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.92,0:09:30.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是  少罗嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.30,0:09:32.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,头会嗡嗡响的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.34,0:09:35.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟 荣太 脸上的伤是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.56,0:09:39.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  这个是给球打了一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.89,0:09:41.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,启作 荣太
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.87,0:09:45.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉酒也腻了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.49,0:09:51.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（你搞什么  你搞什么是在搞什么）
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.28,0:09:54.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,KISS到底有什么意思呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.03,0:09:57.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 但为什么问这种问题呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.66,0:09:58.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是  
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.63,0:10:02.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看似简单却很难回答的问题呢  小夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.91,0:10:04.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然你说去查过了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.71,0:10:05.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.98,0:10:10.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算去图书馆查书 也只查到以前知道的那些
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.72,0:10:13.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎样的做法是知道 也看过别人做
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.37,0:10:15.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.19,0:10:20.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感到别人认为的意思和我所知道的意思好像完全不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.19,0:10:23.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想千草的话一定知道这个的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.57,0:10:26.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小说或文学之类的读过没
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.59,0:10:29.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为阿拉斯拖鲁说过
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.15,0:10:31.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加入个人主观的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.62,0:10:35.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对恰当的分析理性的思索毫无作用
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.19,0:10:41.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿拉斯拖鲁先生好像是在远方代替父亲的人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.85,0:10:43.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拥有很了不起的见解呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.76,0:10:44.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.89,0:10:46.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.74,0:10:49.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是呢  小夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.13,0:11:03.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是呢  小夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.54,0:11:07.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种时候 这样说反而不能理解呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.40,0:11:14.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,资料上所记载的只有现存的事实而已
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.07,0:11:17.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但小夏娜所考虑的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.28,0:11:18.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却是这以外的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.70,0:11:22.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是说模模糊糊没有完整的答案
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.55,0:11:24.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 是关于心和感情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.36,0:11:26.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心和感情 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.42,0:11:33.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你应该知道身体的相互接触是深爱之情的表现吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.63,0:11:36.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 KISS也是其中一种吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.13,0:11:39.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,握手和拥抱之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.35,0:11:40.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都这么做
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.77,0:11:43.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是这样没错
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.90,0:11:47.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好 比如和阿拉斯拖鲁先生这么做的话没关系吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.02,0:11:48.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.90,0:11:50.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那和小悠能做吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.07,0:11:56.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这  这个
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.44,0:12:00.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重新想一下的话 也挺不好意思的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.75,0:12:01.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.16,0:12:04.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是所说内容的中心了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.70,0:12:06.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且说是KISS
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.78,0:12:10.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亲脸颊和嘴对嘴的意思可完全不一样哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.92,0:12:14.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和  和悠二嘴对嘴  
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.26,0:12:19.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不要这样 不想被亲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.98,0:12:22.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.67,0:12:23.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千草  
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.08,0:12:25.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能被亲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.73,0:12:29.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就算是阿拉斯拖鲁先生也不能做的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.44,0:12:32.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.76,0:12:34.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我呢 是这么想的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.42,0:12:38.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘴对嘴的KISS 是像发誓一样的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.81,0:12:39.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发誓 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.45,0:12:43.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 用自己的全部来发誓也没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.16,0:12:46.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把自己的全部托付出去也没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.54,0:12:47.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种发誓的行为
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.72,0:12:49.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是KISS  
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.85,0:13:05.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚就到此为止
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.22,0:13:08.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有点累了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.94,0:13:13.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.44,0:13:14.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.49,0:13:15.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托零时迷子的福
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.12,0:13:19.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的力量每到零点就会恢复吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.12,0:13:21.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那又怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.38,0:13:24.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  就是指不会变老吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.71,0:13:27.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己去确认如何
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.83,0:13:29.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然可能会花很长时间
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.87,0:13:30.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.12,0:13:31.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.11,0:13:35.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会不会和夏娜永远在一起呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.80,0:13:44.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.80,0:13:45.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.64,0:13:49.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有件事要拜托你们两个
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.73,0:14:00.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就行了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.32,0:14:01.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.83,0:14:05.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千草 借下电话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.12,0:14:06.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.16,0:14:09.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但小夏娜 到去学校的时间了哟
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.34,0:14:10.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.75,0:14:13.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.21,0:14:16.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.22,0:14:18.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千草 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.33,0:14:19.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.36,0:14:23.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,换人接了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.67,0:14:25.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.76,0:14:26.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.78,0:14:29.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初次通话 夫人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.36,0:14:32.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在下的名字是阿拉斯拖鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.46,0:14:35.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 原来是阿拉斯拖鲁先生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.02,0:14:39.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平井紫总是承蒙您照顾了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.19,0:14:43.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是坂井悠二的母亲 名叫千草
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.15,0:14:48.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才是 给您添了不少麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.73,0:14:50.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 没什么大不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.40,0:14:56.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那特地来联系究竟有何贵干呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.75,0:14:59.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是平井紫的事 请直说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.62,0:15:05.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 啊  还有那个请称之为夏娜就好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.90,0:15:07.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是这么叫的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.28,0:15:11.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 阿拉斯拖鲁先生也公认了的昵称呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.87,0:15:14.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.29,0:15:17.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有  我想说的是  
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.11,0:15:18.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.14,0:15:21.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实 是昨天的事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.40,0:15:22.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.96,0:15:27.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请稍等
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.02,0:15:28.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小悠小夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.30,0:15:30.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快去学校吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.04,0:15:34.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们走了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.42,0:15:35.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.85,0:15:37.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快走啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.17,0:15:41.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.83,0:15:46.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并不是否定夫人的恋爱观
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.71,0:15:49.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像昨天的那些话请不要说了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.99,0:15:52.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小夏娜说出去了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.34,0:15:56.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 是我硬逼着她说出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.99,0:16:01.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不论何时 能听到那个小夏娜说这些的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.49,0:16:05.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是被深深信赖着的证据呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.58,0:16:06.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.09,0:16:10.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来小夏娜是被很重视地抚养长大的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.55,0:16:13.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是非常单纯的好孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.63,0:16:14.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.92,0:16:15.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因为如此
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.32,0:16:22.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会诱发夏娜像昨天一样和坂井悠二欠考虑的接触的发言
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.81,0:16:24.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请尽量小心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.18,0:16:27.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您的意思我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.41,0:16:29.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夫人非常明白事理
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.48,0:16:33.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样一来就能全交给您了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.05,0:16:34.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.68,0:16:35.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.68,0:16:36.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了小夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.29,0:16:40.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以再和您谈谈吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.03,0:16:42.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.65,0:16:44.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小夏娜和说的一样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.19,0:16:47.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是个高贵而又厉害的好孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.31,0:16:53.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我以为在另一方面却有着非常幼小而脆弱的部分
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.91,0:16:58.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请继续
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.82,0:17:00.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 那失礼的说一句
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.13,0:17:09.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我感到小夏娜对人的感情和心都很陌生 有着毫无防备之处
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.05,0:17:12.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我家的悠二是第一次
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.91,0:17:15.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,困扰年轻人的东西出现时
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.10,0:17:19.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那纯真无垢的孩子会多么抵触呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.31,0:17:22.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天我感觉到了这危险
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.57,0:17:25.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才说了那些话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.97,0:17:28.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是  还太早了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.25,0:17:33.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想花上数年时间 让她经历各种事情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.24,0:17:37.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后慢慢地告诉她会比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.79,0:17:41.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻烦不会由我们随心所欲地发生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.37,0:17:42.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.44,0:17:46.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 我想教她应该教的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.23,0:17:49.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不会有太早这说法的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.34,0:17:52.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也为了小夏娜自己
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.13,0:17:59.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且女孩子可是比外观看起来早熟很多的哟
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.94,0:18:03.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夫人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.30,0:18:04.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.54,0:18:10.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我之前所做的不适当的发言可以撤回么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.99,0:18:11.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.01,0:18:13.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说了大言不惭的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.45,0:18:16.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小夏娜的话没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.72,0:18:18.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要好好教她的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.68,0:18:23.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就应该会从内心找到属于自己的做法和正确答案的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.92,0:18:25.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种信赖应该有吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.02,0:18:28.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.63,0:18:39.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.93,0:18:42.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,近了 好近啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.77,0:18:46.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.53,0:18:48.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像在找什么东西似的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.82,0:18:49.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.13,0:18:53.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 不愧是索拉特的「欲望的嗅觉」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.06,0:18:55.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种令人厌烦的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.88,0:18:57.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定是火焰之雾了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.79,0:18:59.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 哪里哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.52,0:19:00.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.46,0:19:02.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火焰之雾 好想要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.88,0:19:04.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有一点
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.67,0:19:07.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多要给察觉到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.40,0:19:09.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 也罢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.94,0:19:14.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你应该明白火焰之雾的出现只是时间问题
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.02,0:19:15.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  打算如何
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.26,0:19:20.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再设些机关 以防万一
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.68,0:19:23.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始吧 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.48,0:19:24.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.30,0:19:29.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一步 先去打个招呼如何
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.05,0:19:32.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为要找出来  是很简单的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.76,0:19:42.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天发生了什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.38,0:19:45.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 刚才阿拉斯拖鲁在电话里说
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.24,0:19:47.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天的事怎么怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.83,0:19:49.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.77,0:19:54.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.46,0:19:55.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.42,0:19:58.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你绝对绝对不做
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.52,0:20:03.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.43,0:20:07.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以的话 做了坂井同学的份  
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.80,0:20:09.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.16,0:20:12.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为一直都吃饭团
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.02,0:20:13.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个  
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.94,0:20:15.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.24,0:20:17.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.14,0:20:20.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.74,0:20:21.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.72,0:20:26.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从哪个开始吃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.96,0:20:28.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真伤脑筋呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.98,0:20:42.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀  买了不少呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.03,0:20:43.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岂止「不少」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.37,0:20:45.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.66,0:20:47.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,购物才刚开始啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.52,0:20:58.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是在青黄不接时又来了大客户
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.92,0:21:00.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些家伙是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.21,0:21:02.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大姐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.64,0:21:12.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不见了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.31,0:21:14.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美丽的杀戮者
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.48,0:21:17.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这种地方干嘛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.65,0:21:19.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靠不住的色男
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.72,0:21:21.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 认识的 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.52,0:21:24.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 给你介绍一下 泰莉亚露
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.89,0:21:27.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在火焰之雾里也屈指可数的杀手
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.26,0:21:31.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悼词的咏唱者——玛丘莉·顿
